Now, components and fig-ma allow you to reuse certain elements.

00:16:43.210 --> 00:16:53.965
Making any changes to the parent component will change the child components as well.

00:16:53.965 --> 00:16:59.620
If I were to duplicate this component in another page and I would make changes to

00:16:59.620 --> 00:17:06.285
this master instance those changes will be reflected in the other pages as well.

00:17:06.285 --> 00:17:09.735
Now that I have that turned into a component,

00:17:09.735 --> 00:17:13.435
I can select it and I can rotate it.

